text: Andrus Ansip (born 1 October 1956) is an Estonian politician. He was the Prime Minister of Estonia from 2005 to 2014.The Government of the Republic of Estonia: Andrus Ansip - Estonian Government He is chairman of the market liberal Estonian Reform Party (). ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Estonia Category:MEPs for Estonia
